<h2>Our Core Values</h2>
<div id="myCarousel" style="height:225px;" class="carousel slide text-center" data-ride="carousel">

    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active" style="background-color:grey;"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1" style="background-color:grey;"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2" style="background-color:grey;"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="3" style="background-color:grey;"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="4" style="background-color:grey;"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="5" style="background-color:grey;"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="6" style="background-color:grey;"></li>
    </ol>


    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
        <div class="item active">
            <h3>Commit to Delivery Excellence</h3><br><h4><span style="font-style:normal;">We have a passion for consulting excellence. In all of our projects, we strive to first<br>understand your needs and then deliver on our commitments 100 percent of the time.</span></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h3>Embrace Integrity and Openness</h3><br><h4><span style="font-style:normal;">We value strong, positive relationships that<br /> are open and honest. This differentiates us and allows<br /> us to accomplish much more than we would be able to otherwise.</span></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h3>Practice Responsible Stewardship</h3><br><h4><span style="font-style:normal;">We value stewardship and fiscal accountability and always strive to do more with less.<br /> We guard and conserve company resources as if they were our own because<br /> it makes good business sense at all times, not just during lean times.</span></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h3>Invest in an Exceptional Culture</h3><br><h4><span style="font-style:normal;">We aim to hire and retain talented people from diverse backgrounds who can create a<br /> high impact for our clients and internally within our company.</span></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h3>Ignite Passion for the greater good</h3><br><h4><span style="font-style:normal;">We take pride in our commitment to improving the world in which we live and actively preserving<br /> our environment for future generations. We are steadfast in our devotion to the communities<br /> we serve and actively promote employee involvement in community improvement projects.</span></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h3>Strive to Innovate</h3><br><h4><span style="font-style:normal;">We value passion, determination, perseverance, and innovation.<br /> We are inspired because we believe in what we are doing and where we are going.<br /> We believe in using innovation to remove obstacles and help you succeed.</span></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <h3>Live a Balanced Life</h3><br><h4><span style="font-style:normal;">Our employees are our greatest asset. Because of that, we encourage our <br />people to strive for balance in their life, and we monitor projects<br /> to ensure our employees have time for family, community and personal interests.</span></h4>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Left and right controls -->
    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
</div>







